{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Routers","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/routers","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>routers</strong> 是指路由器。在 Web 有兩種意思：</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>針對網路層，路由器是一種決定<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">封包</a>去向的網路設備。路由器是由 retailer 分發，允許用戶與網際網路互動。</li>\n  <li>針對應用層的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/SPA\">SPA</a>，路由器是一種透過給定的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/URL\">URL</a> 來決定頁面如何呈現的函式庫。這個中間件（middleware）會藉由給定 URL 給檔案生成需要的路徑、以渲染下一頁的所需內容。</li>\n</ol>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一般知識","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<p>針對網路層：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">路由器</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>針對應用層，訪間熱門的 SPA 框架都有自己的路由器函式庫：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/router\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Angular router</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://reacttraining.com/react-router\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">React router</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://router.vuejs.org\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Vue router</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"routers 是指路由器。在 Web 有兩種意思：","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Routers","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Router (ルーター)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/routers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/routers/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/routers","title":"Routers"}],"pageTitle":"Routers - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}